      <title>德国即将举行提前投票，能源目标面临阻碍</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/germany-s-looming-snap-vote-throws-wrench-into-energy-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近年来，高昂的能源成本和向清洁燃料转型的不确定性是德国工业巨头外流的主要原因。执政联盟的突然解散和迫在眉睫的提前选举将使这一问题更加难以解决。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/germany-s-looming-snap-vote-throws-wrench-into-energy-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 12:08:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
