      <title>交易员权衡特朗普的影响，大选震动后油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于交易员权衡唐纳德·特朗普的大选胜利对原油市场可能产生的影响，美元停止了大选后的上涨，油价在周三经历了过山车式波动后出现下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-nov-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Nov 2024 23:28:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
